{"id":232937661,"title":"這三種書挑選~求推薦","content":"本身英文程度不算好記性也不是看一遍就會\n要一直練習手寫與口唸個1~3遍才記得\n現在想買個可以好好練的扎實的書\n有去看過評價挑出來這三種\n想請大家給我意見謝謝\n\n選手1(完全圖解1小時學會英文文法)\n優：\n圖畫活潑易懂\n缺：\n沒有時態章節\n內容初級只教文法\nhttp://i.imgur.com/5wWG5Dw.jpg\n選手2(新概念全方位英語)\n優：\n標準美式發音(?\n內容比較全方位\n有分初級中級高級\n缺：\n找不到評價\nhttp://i.imgur.com/vayRDa4.jpg\n選手3(劍橋活用英語文法套書)\n優：\n文法寫的詳細\n有豐富練習題反饋\n沒有太多中文專有名詞\n缺：\n內容有小部分問題\n初級跟中級差不多(中級只是更詳細點)\nhttp://i.imgur.com/io2oOrj.jpg\n\n\n大家如果有推薦適合打好基礎的書也推薦一下\n在這邊先感謝你們了~!","excerpt":"本身英文程度不算好記性也不是看一遍就會，要一直練習手寫與口唸個1~3遍才記得，現在想買個可以好好練的扎實的書，有去看過評價挑出來這三種，想請大家給我意見謝謝，選手1（完全圖解1小時學會英文文法），優：","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"ecc6a486-c4ac-4f76-996d-7dda5dcb8518","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-22T09:03:29.117Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-22T09:03:29.117Z","commentCount":5,"likeCount":3,"tags":[],"topics":["英文","英語","自學","書籍"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"語言","forumAlias":"language","school":"東南科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":3}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/5wWG5Dw.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/vayRDa4.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/io2oOrj.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"972e4e38-0205-4407-8dcb-3b1676f9c78d","url":"https://i.imgur.com/5wWG5Dwl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/5wWG5Dwl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/5wWG5Dwl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-22T09:03:29.117Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-22T09:03:29.117Z"},{"id":"972e4e38-0205-4407-8dcb-3b1676f9c78d","url":"http://i.imgur.com/5wWG5Dw.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/5wWG5Dw","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/5wWG5Dwl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-22T